snippet.title: A Little to the Left - Release Date Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: A Little to the Left received a release date during the Future Games Show. Max Inferno’s cosy Kondo-esque tidying puzzler is coming, mischievous cats and all, to PC and Mac on November 8 later this year.
